<style>
table {
  font-family: arial, sans-serif;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  width: 100%;
}

td, th {
  border: 1px solid #dddddd;
  text-align: left;
  padding: 8px;
}

tr:nth-child(even) {
  background-color: #dddddd;
}
</style>


Hi <%=@user.username%>! Here are all the tickets the team is working on.<br>
<br>
<a href=create_tickets>create ticket</a><br>
<br>


Here are your team's tickets:<br>
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Ticket ID</th>
        <th>Ticket Title</th>
        <th>Ticket Details</th>
        <th>Owned By</th>
        <th>Created At</th>
        <th>Updated At</th>
    </tr>
    <% @user.tickets.each do |ticket| %>
        <tr>
        <td><%=ticket.id%></td>
        <td><%=ticket.title%></td>
        <td><%=ticket.details%></td>
        <td><%=ticket.employee.username%></td>
        <td><%=ticket.created_at%></td>
        <td><%=ticket.updated_at%></td>
        </tr>
    <%end%>
</table>
